default2. Bioplastics in mixeddefault waste streamsdefault default&#xa0;defaultModern waste recovery systems
default cope with intermingled materials, including a 
defaultvariety of different polymer types. 
defaultA
defaultutomated plant
defaults
default sort out
default the
default profitable parts of the 
defaultw
defaultaste stream (for example PE, or PET)
